(185, 27, 74, 'Retinol + Complete Anti-Aging Facial Moisturizer Cream with Hyaluronic Acid & Breakthrough Anti Wrinkle Complex - For Face and Eye Area', 'OUR BIG 3 ANTI-AGING INGREDIENTS - Combines the time-tested benefits of high-grade retinol and hyaluronic acid with Fision Wrinkle Fix, an advanced anti aging complex that has shown extraordinary clinical results. Together with rich base ingredients, this blend deeply hydrates while renewing and defending skin from visible signs of aging, including wrinkles, fine lines & age spots.\r\n\r\nHYDRATE, RESTORE & PROTECT - Retinol, hyaluronic acid and FisionWrinkle Fix reduce wrinkle depth, fine lines and age spots, while rich base ingredients provide intense hydration while soothing and protecting skin from aging caused by UV and free radical exposure.\r\n\r\nIRRITATION-FREE RETINOL - Our cream is designed to provide maximum anti-aging benefits without causing drying, peeling, redness and other irritation that is common among creams containing retinol. Our base formulation is loaded with natural soothing, hydrating and heeling ingredients to counteract the irritation that may result from daily application of retinol.\r\n\r\nTHE SCIENCE OF FISION WRINKLE FIX - Plant peptides and Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid bind together to promote remarkable enhancements in cellular vitality and the skin’s ability to produce hyaluronic acid to fill in wrinkles.\r\n\r\nLAB TESTS & CLINICAL TRIALS - In lab tests Fision Wrinkle Fix has vastly outperformed a Vitamin C (the non-RX benchmark for anti-aging) in cellular viability and hyaluronic acid synthesis. Fision showed a 25x increase in the ability to promote hyaluronic acid synthesis and a 13% increase in cellular vitality vs. Vitamin C. Fision also produced over 50% more hyaluronic acid synthesis than Glycolic Acid, a known HA booster. In a 56-day clinical trial of adult females, Fision showed an average decrease of 20% in wrinkle depth. A notable reduction in age spots was also realized.