(259, 8, 67, 'ODODOS High Waist Out Pocket Yoga Pants Tummy Control Workout Running 4 Way Stretch Yoga Leggings', 'Every piece of ODODOS Yoga we design comes from our practice—what we need and want, always with the goal of perfecting forward, contemporary pieces that work from studio to street.\r\n\r\nYoga wear is ubiquitous today. We see it in the gym for workouts, in the studio for Pilates, in the grocery store and even in casual restaurants and coffee shops. It’s part of the casualization of America.', 'ododos-high-waist-out-pocket-yoga-pants-tummy-control-workout-running-4-way-stretch-yoga-leggings-47', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61VjFfUU2zL._UY679_.jpg', '19.98', '', '', '', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0711Y2K4Z/ref=as_li_ss_tl?psc=1&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=d4424e496e4681e58d052eea2cf447d8', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Yoga Pants', 'yoga-pants', 'ODODOS High Waist Out Pocket Yoga Pants Tummy Control Workout Running 4 Way Stretch Yoga Leggings', 'Every piece of ODODOS Yoga we design comes from our practice—what we need and want, always with the goal of perfecting forward, contemporary pieces that work from studio to street.  Yoga wear is ubiquitous today. We see it in the gym for workouts, in the studio for Pilates, in the grocery store and even in casual restaurants and coffee shops. It’s part of the casualization of America.', 1, '', 'ODODOS ', 4, '4,498+ customer reviews', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0711Y2K4Z/ref=as_li_ss_tl?psc=1&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=d4424e496e4681e58d052eea2cf447d8#customerReviews', '165+ answered questions', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0711Y2K4Z/ref=as_li_ss_tl?psc=1&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=d4424e496e4681e58d052eea2cf447d8#Ask', 1, 1, '2018-10-06 03:52:29', '2018-10-06 03:52:29'),
(260, 8, 67, 'Simple Modern Summit Water Bottle + Extra Lid - Wide Mouth Vacuum Insulated 18/8 Stainless Steel Powder Coated - 8 Sizes, 24 Colors', 'Vacuum Insulation Technology\r\n\r\nThis bottle has a double-wall exterior with a vacuum seal between the walls. This means your drink temperature has no medium for the heat or cold to transfer through. Your drink will truly stay as hot or cold as long as possible. Retire your coasters and koozies. Even filled with ice or boiling water, this bottle will never sweat or get hot to the touch!\r\n\r\nCopper Coated Insulation\r\n\r\nThe exterior of the vacuum sealed area is dipped in copper for added insulation. Copper reduces the transfer of temperature, adding even more insulation to your bottle. The BPA-free stainless steel lid is also insulated against heat transfer.\r\n\r\nPremium 18/8 Stainless Steel\r\n\r\nSimple Modern insulated water bottles are made of high quality food grade 18/8 stainless steel metal. The bottle is highly rust resistant and it will not retain flavors from previous drinks like plastic bottles will. All Simple Modern bottles, tumblers, and lids are BPA free. Hand wash only.\r\n\r\nDurable Powder Coating\r\n\r\nEnjoy the protection and color that rugged powder coating adds to the bottle. The powder coating is sleek and durable, making it the perfect travel companion.\r\n\r\nWide Mouth Opening\r\n\r\nThe wide mouth opening on all Summit water bottles allows for easy filling and cleaning. Almost any size of ice cube fits through the opening. The Summit has 5 different lid types that fit every size of the bottle.', 'simple-modern-summit-water-bottle-extra-lid--wide-mouth-vacuum-insulated-188-stainless-steel-powder-coated--8-sizes-24-colors', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41jyPjKh-yL._SX679_.jpg', '11.99 - 37', '', '', '', 'https://www.amazon.com/Simple-Modern-Summit-Water-Bottle/dp/B07DMFKTK4/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&refRID=VC9111RZF0C9K5V6X1M8&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-2