(309, 35, 0, 'The 5 Love Languages Singles Edition: The Secret that Will Revolutionize Your Relationships Paperback – January 3, 2017', 'Nothing has more potential for enhancing one’s sense of well-being than effectively loving and being loved. This book is designed to help you do both of these things effectively.”\r\n—Gary Chapman\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nWith more than 8 million copies sold, The 5 Love Languages® continues to strengthen relationships worldwide. Although originally crafted with married couples in mind, the love languages have proven themselves to be universal. Whether it’s dating relationships, parents, coworkers, or friends—understanding your unique love language and that of others can significantly improve your relationships.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe premise is simple: Different people with different personalities express love in different ways. Therefore, if you want to give and receive love most effectively, you’ve got to learn to speak the right language.', 'the-5-love-languages-singles-edition-the-secret-that-will-revolutionize-your-relationships-paperback-january-3-2017', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51lP1GwvImL._SX321_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg', '11.97', '', '', '', 'https://www.amazon.com/Love-Languages-Singles-Revolutionize-Relationships/dp/0802414818/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&pd_rd_i=0802414818&pd_rd_r=e1dc8c26-ca4d-11e8-9abb-7d2cd28fbd32&pd_rd_w=t8NqR&pd_rd_wg=EiZWi&pf_rd_i=desktop-dp-sims&pf_rd_m=ATVPDKIKX0DER&pf_rd_p=18bb0b78-4200-49b9-ac91-f141d61a17', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Book', 'book', 'The 5 Love Languages Singles Edition: The Secret that Will Revolutionize Your Relationships Paperback – January 3, 2017', 'Nothing has more potential for enhancing one’s sense of well-being than effectively loving and being loved. This book is designed to help you do both of these things effectively.” —Gary Chapman     With more than 8 million copies sold, The 5 Love Languages® continues to strengthen relationships worldwide. Although origin