(331, 4, 24, 'ODODOS High Waist Out Pocket Yoga Pants Tummy Control Workout Running 4 Way Stretch Yoga Leggings', 'Every piece of ODODOS Yoga we design comes from our practice—what we need and want, always with the goal of perfecting forward, contemporary pieces that work from studio to street.\r\n\r\nYoga wear is ubiquitous today. We see it in the gym for workouts, in the studio for Pilates, in the grocery store and even in casual restaurants and coffee shops. It’s part of the casualization of America. ', 'ododos-high-waist-out-pocket-yoga-pants-tummy-control-workout-running-4-way-stretch-yoga-leggings-', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61vC1VfsXhL._UX569_.jpg', '18.98 - 20', '', '', '', 'https://www.amazon.com/ODODOS-Control-Workout-Running-Leggings/dp/B07BYKLLZN/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&refRID=3BAK9DSHB0SN5H2S2QCW&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=f06ae3df15fac8bacce81fa9295bd24d&language=en_US', 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Leggings', 'leggings', 'ODODOS High Waist Out Pocket Yoga Pants Tummy Control Workout Running 4 Way Stretch Yoga Leggings | Best Seller', 'Every piece of ODODOS Yoga we design comes from our practice—what we need and want, always with the goal of perfecting forward, contemporary pieces that work from studio to street.  Yoga wear is ubiquitous today. We see it in the gym for workouts, in the studio for Pilates, in the grocery store and even in casual restaurants and coffee shops. It’s part of the casualization of America. ', 1, '', ' ODODOS', 4, '4,516+ customer reviews', 'https://www.amazon.com/ODODOS-Control-Workout-Running-Leggings/dp/B07BYKLLZN/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&refRID=3BAK9DSHB0SN5H2S2QCW&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=f06ae3df15fac8bacce81fa9295bd24d&language=en_US#customerReviews', '168+ answered questions', 'https://www.amazon.com/ODODOS-Control-Workout-Running-Leggings/dp/B07BYKLLZN/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&refRID=3BAK9DSHB0SN5H2S2QCW&linkCode=ll1&tag=getconsumerpr-20&linkId=f06ae3d